Class Node

  • java.lang.Object
    • javafx.scene.control.TreeItem<Node>
      • Node
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    javafx.event.EventTarget

    public class Node
extends javafx.scene.control.TreeItem<Node>
    Object class for a Node. A Node is a single piece of data the encapsulates the path, name, number of files, size of contents, and children of a directory.
    Author:
    Andre Fernandez
